  "uuid": "ff02efc7819dc0f138064620d4a8d6cf",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "F&B SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>We are expanding and we are looking for a dedicated <strong>F&amp;B Outlet Supervisor</strong> to assist our Outlet Manager in overseeing operations at our new outlet. If you have a strong background in food and beverage management and a passion for customer service, we want you to join our team.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist the Outlet Manager in overseeing overall outlet operations to ensure a smooth and efficient operation</li>\n  <li>Supervise staff, manage schedules, and provide training and guidance to maintain team performance</li>\n  <li>Ensure the POS system runs smoothly, handle transactions, and assist with orders as needed</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with HR, Finance, and Marketing departments to achieve business goals</li>\n  <li>Uphold cleanliness, quality, and service standards for excellent customer satisfaction</li>\n  <li>Assist in sourcing and managing tenants for new  outlet locations</li>\n  <li>Adhere to company policies and ensure operations      are in compliance with set standards and regulations</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Pre-requisites:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven experience in F&amp;B management with a  focus on outlet operations</li>\n  <li>Strong leadership skills and the ability to  motivate and support a team</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with SGdataPOS and Infotech knowledge is an advantage but not a must.</li>\n  <li>Ability to collaborate with various departments to drive business success</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, organizational, and problem-solving skills</li>\n  <li>Willingness to work long hours, including weekends and public holidays</li>\n  <li>Commitment to adhering to Company policies and maintaining high operational standards</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>由于我们的业务扩展，我们正在寻找一位充满热情且经验丰富的<strong>餐饮店主管</strong>，协助店长管理我们的新店。如果你具备餐饮管理经验，热衷于提供卓越的客户服务，并能在快节奏的环境中表现出色，我们诚邀你加入我们的团队！</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>主要职责：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>协助店长监督店铺运营，确保日常运营顺利进行</li>\n  <li>管理员工，制定排班计划并进行培训，确保团队的高效运作</li>\n  <li>确保POS系统顺畅运行，处理交易并协助订单管理</li>\n  <li>与人力资源、财务、市场等部门密切合作，共同达成业务目标</li>\n  <li>保持高标准的卫生、质量和服务，确保顾客满意</li>\n  <li>协助寻找租户并参与新店铺位置的租赁事务</li>\n  <li>遵守公司政策，确保所有运营符合公司标准和规定</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>具备条件：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>具有餐饮管理（F&amp;B）经验，尤其是在店铺运营方面</li>\n  <li>强大的领导力和团队管理能力，能够激励和支持团队</li>\n  <li>熟悉POS系统（了解SGdataPOS和Infotech系统者优先，但非必须）</li>\n  <li>能够与各部门合作，推动业务成功</li>\n  <li>出色的沟通、组织和问题解决能力</li>\n  <li><strong>愿意工作长时间，包括周末和公共假期</strong></li>\n  <li>坚持遵守公司政策，确保高效的运营管理</li>\n</ul>",
  "minimumYearsExperience": 2,
